events.title: Feeding ducks
events.borderColor: Come hang out and feed ducks with your brothers.  We will be going to Washington Park; bring your own bread.

events.title: Treasure House of Hope
events.borderColor: We will be bagging, labeling, and putting ribbons on 500-600 loaves of banana, pumpkin and zucchini breads. Sometimes we will have boxes of bananas that we are smashing or zucchini that we puree.  Please wear clothing you don't mind getting dirty and wear closed-toed shoes. We have hair nets and aprons but if you have a hat you'd like to wear that's fine.  You will be working with nuts

events.title: Group Launch and Pizza
events.borderColor: Come complete the first of the LEADS courses, Launch! The webinar is individual, but we can discuss any questions and help each other out :) Also there will be pizza!!
